No.

946
01:10:02,900 --> 01:10:08,580
You know, l never believed
that anyone could love me for me.

947
01:10:10,460 --> 01:10:14,060
How could l,
when my own mother didn't?

948
01:10:15,700 --> 01:10:17,380
She didn't?

949
01:10:17,580 --> 01:10:20,420
She left me and my brother at a...

950
01:10:23,820 --> 01:10:27,140
..at a home in Albany when l was three.

951
01:10:27,340 --> 01:10:31,100
No note, no nothing.
Never asked about us.

952
01:10:31,300 --> 01:10:33,660
Never said, ''l'm sorry.''

953
01:10:38,540 --> 01:10:40,780
Your mother has to love you.

954
01:10:41,820 --> 01:10:42,980
Right Danny?

955
01:10:43,180 --> 01:10:48,260
So even if no one else does,
she has to, doesn't she?

956
01:10:50,900 --> 01:10:54,220
Well, if my own mother
couldn't love me, l...

957
01:11:01,820 --> 01:11:03,620
I...

958
01:11:06,700 --> 01:11:09,220
l love you, Uncle Joe.

959
01:11:12,460 --> 01:11:14,220
You do?

960
01:11:15,580 --> 01:11:17,740
Yeah, l do.

961
01:11:21,300 --> 01:11:23,380
Take me home, Danny.

962
01:11:27,220 --> 01:11:29,980
[Robin] Danny what do you mean
